headline.print_headline: Israeli Police Officers Kill Two Palestinian Men
headline.main: Israeli Police Officers Kill Two Palestinian Men

snippet: The shooting occurred around midnight on Friday near the Zayyim checkpoint on the outskirts of East Jerusalem in the West Bank.
abstract: Israeli police officers kill two Palestinian men in two separate incidents; both men attacked officers with knives, one in West Bank and second in East Jerusalem; attacks are latest in spate by Palestinians who appear to be acting alone.
